    <S id="S1">
        <FORM>kidi katta ni-he-lan ti Jesus pa-mut, dou lummad-ato makka Ju-dea mou-qua tou Galilæa.</FORM>
    </S>
    <S id="S2">
        <FORM>Ka rarymma ki lbægh ki soulat.</FORM>
    </S>
    <S id="S3">
        <FORM>1. SIæugh ki anna ni-akoumea ki 'Ouvavatoug-han ki Jo-den, ka ni-sa-bavau ta ti Jesus mou-qua tou Jerusalem.</FORM>
    </S>
    <S id="S4">
        <FORM>2 Ka akoumea hynna tou Je-rusalem i toutouk [ki ngataf] ki i-ouko ta ǣiæu'ug-han ka ra-loum ka- si-ouä tou sou ki He-breen Bethesda, ka narymmato kisau-lan ka laf.</FORM>
    </S>
    <S id="S5">
        <FORM>3 Ka ni-malikou hynna ta ka-batoung-an ka irang ka maälam, ka mavoutta, ka mapyllei, ka yhgou yl-lan tou 'amamat-ten kik'yllyk ka Iykka-eih ki raloum.</FORM>
    </S>
    <S id="S6">
        <FORM>4 Ka Tama: Gnau ta ni-mou-rarim tou sasasat ki kidi tou-'ǣi-æug-han tmyvo ki raloum: anna ta ti-mamang ta nisi-ouro hynna mou-rbo rou t'yvou-an-nato ta raloum ni-kæuh d'arijk kagh ta teni, mou-kouna rou kamamang lava ta maälam tyn.</FORM>
    </S>
    <S id="S7">
        <FORM>5 Ka ni-akoumea hynna saät ki voual ka makka touro kyttiæn æb ki kæu-'yhpa ki tauwil ki ni-kaälam-men tyn.</FORM>
    </S>
    <S id="S8">
        <FORM>6 Irou ka kmytta ta ti Jesus ty-ni-æn ka malykko, ka kavan-nan</FORM>
    </S>
</TEXT>
